column2: SELECT s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberID, s.class, s.survey, s.z, s.zErr, sp.ra, sp.dec, sp.cModelMag_u - sp.extinction_u as mag_u, sp.cModelMag_g - sp.extinction_g as mag_g, sp.cModelMag_r - sp.extinction_r as mag_r, sp.cModelMag_i - sp.extinction_i as mag_i, sp.cModelMag_z - sp.extinction_z as mag_z FROM SpecObj AS s JOIN SpecPhoto AS sp ON sp.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE AND (s.Class = #) AND s.zwarning = #
